      findings: [`${d.duplicateIpRows.length} duplicate IP group(s) and ${d.duplicateDeviceRows.length} impacted device record(s) were returned.`],
      conclusion: "Duplicate identity evidence should be confirmed and cleaned to avoid inventory overcounting."
